            <h5 class="fw-bold mt-2 mb-3">1. Introduction</h5>
            <p class="text-muted">Trusted Escort India ("we", "us", "our") operates the website <strong>listtrusted.vercel.app</strong>. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose and safeguard your information when you visit our website. Please read it carefully.</p>

            <h5 class="fw-bold mt-4 mb-3">2. Information We Collect</h5>
            <p class="text-muted"><strong>a) Information you provide directly:</strong> When you register an account or post an advertisement you provide your name, email address, phone number and profile content. This information is stored securely in our database.</p>
            <p class="text-muted"><strong>b) Automatically collected information:</strong> When you browse our site, we may collect IP addresses, browser type, device information, pages visited and referral URLs via standard server logs. We do not use advertising trackers or third-party analytics that sell your data.</p>
            <p class="text-muted"><strong>c) Images:</strong> Ad images are uploaded to Cloudinary, a third-party secure cloud storage provider. We do not store images on our own servers.</p>

            <h5 class="fw-bold mt-4 mb-3">3. How We Use Your Information</h5>
            <ul class="text-muted ps-3">
              <li class="mb-2">To create and manage your account.</li>
              <li class="mb-2">To display your advertisement listings (only approved ads are shown publicly).</li>
              <li class="mb-2">To send administrative emails (account notifications, ad approvals/rejections).</li>
              <li class="mb-2">To enforce our Terms and Conditions and investigate abuse reports.</li>
              <li class="mb-2">To improve site performance and user experience.</li>
            </ul>

            <h5 class="fw-bold mt-4 mb-3">4. Information Sharing</h5>
            <p class="text-muted">We <strong>do not sell, rent or trade</strong> your personal information to any third party. Information may be shared only:</p>
            <ul class="text-muted ps-3">
              <li class="mb-2">With our hosting and infrastructure providers (Vercel, MongoDB Atlas, Cloudinary) strictly for operating the service.</li>
              <li class="mb-2">When required by law or a valid court order.</li>
              <li class="mb-2">To prevent fraud, protect safety or report human trafficking to the relevant authorities.</li>
            </ul>

            <h5 class="fw-bold mt-4 mb-3">5. Cookies</h5>
            <p class="text-muted">We use session cookies to keep you logged in. These are essential functional cookies and are deleted when you close your browser or log out. We do not use advertising or tracking cookies.</p>

            <h5 class="fw-bold mt-4 mb-3">6. Data Security</h5>
            <p class="text-muted">We implement industry-standard security measures including encrypted connections (HTTPS), hashed passwords and access controls. However, no transmission over the internet is 100% secure. You use our platform at your own risk.</p>

            <h5 class="fw-bold mt-4 mb-3">7. Data Retention</h5>
            <p class="text-muted">Account data is retained for as long as your account is active. Deleted accounts and their associated ads are purged within 30 days. You may request deletion of your data at any time by contacting <a href="mailto:support@listtrusted.vercel.app">support@listtrusted.vercel.app</a>.</p>

            <h5 class="fw-bold mt-4 mb-3">8. Children's Privacy</h5>
            <p class="text-muted">This website is strictly for adults aged 18 and above. We do not knowingly collect information from anyone under 18. If you believe a minor has registered, contact us immediately at <a href="mailto:abuse@listtrusted.vercel.app">abuse@listtrusted.vercel.app</a>.</p>

            <h5 class="fw-bold mt-4 mb-3">9. Changes to This Policy</h5>
            <p class="text-muted">We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated date. Continued use of the site after changes constitutes your acceptance.</p>

            <h5 class="fw-bold mt-4 mb-3">10. Contact Us</h5>
